[section#valarray.range
    [:en] Range access
    [:zh_CN] 范围访问
]

[para]
[:en] The [`iterator] type is a type that meets the requirements of a mutable
[^:oc RandomAccessIterator] ([#random.access.iterators]) and models
[`:c contiguous_iterator] ([#iterator.concept.contiguous]).
[:zh_CN] 类型 [`iterator] 为满足对可改动 [^:oc RandomAccessIterator] 的规定（[#random.access.iterators]）
并构成 [`:c contiguous_iterator]（[#iterator.concept.contiguous]）的类型。

[:en] Its [`value_type] is the template parameter [`T] and its [`reference] type is [`T&].
[:zh_CN] 其 [`value_type] 为模板形参 [`T]，且其 [`reference] 类型为 [`T&]。

[:en] The [`const_iterator] type meets the requirements of a constant
[^:oc RandomAccessIterator] and models [`:c contiguous_iterator].
[:zh_CN] [`const_iterator] 类型满足对常量 [^:oc RandomAccessIterator] 的规定并构成
[`:c contiguous_iterator]。

[:en] Its [`value_type] is the template parameter [`T] and its [`reference] type is [`const T&].
[:zh_CN] 其 [`value_type] 为模板形参 [`T]，且其 [`reference] 类型为 [`const T&]。

[para]
[:en] The iterators returned by [`begin] and [`end] for an array are guaranteed
to be valid until the member function [`resize(size_t, T)] ([#valarray.members])
is called for that array or until the lifetime of that array ends, whichever happens first.
[:zh_CN] 由 [`begin] 和 [`end] 在一个数组上所返回的迭代器，保证直到对该数组调用
成员函数 [`resize(size_t, T)]（[#valarray.members]），或者这个数组的生存期结束
（二者首先发生者为准）之前一直有效。

[%@lib@member begin[!valarray]]
[codeblock:declaration]
iterator begin();
const_iterator begin() const;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] An iterator referencing the first value in the array.
[:zh_CN] 指代数组中的第一个值的迭代器。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member end[!valarray]]
[codeblock:declaration]
iterator end();
const_iterator end() const;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] An iterator referencing one past the last value in the array.
[:zh_CN] 指代越过数组中的最后一个值的位置的迭代器。
[div:end]
